# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok with their hands clasped to their hearts , democratic and republican members of congress stood shoulder to shoulder on the steps of the capitol on monday evening and sang `` the star-spangled banner , '' in a ceremony echoing a spontaneous moment on the evening of the #### attacks .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (s / stand-01
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (p / person
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (g / government-organization
                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "Congress"))
                              :ARG2 (m / member))
                        :mod (d / democratic))
                  :op2 (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (p3 / political-party
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Republican"))
                              :ARG2 (m2 / member)))
                  :part (h3 / hand)
                  :part (h4 / heart))
            :ARG2 (s2 / step
                  :part-of (c / capitol))
            :manner (s3 / shoulder-to-shoulder)
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (m3 / monday)
                  :dayperiod (e / evening)))
      :op2 (s4 / sing-01
            :ARG0 a2
            :ARG1 (b / banner
                  :ARG1-of (s5 / spangle-01
                        :ARG2 (s6 / star)))
            :manner (c2 / ceremony
                  :ARG1-of (e2 / echo-01
                        :ARG2 (m4 / moment
                              :mod (s7 / spontaneous)
                              :time (d3 / date-entity
                                    :dayperiod (e3 / evening
                                          :mod (a3 / attack-01))))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

# ::alignments
(f / fall-01
      :ARG1 (s / stock
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Japan")))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday))
      :ARG0-of (e / end-01
            :ARG1 (r / rally-01
                  :duration (t2 / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 3
                        :unit (d2 / day))))
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (t3 / take-01
                  :ARG0 (p / person
                        :ARG0-of (t4 / trade-01))
                  :ARG1 (c3 / cue
                        :poss p)
                  :ARG2 (f2 / fall-01
                        :ARG1 (m / market-sector
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Wall"
                                    :op2 "Street"))
                        :time (o / overnight))
                  :concession (r2 / remain-01
                        :ARG1 p
                        :ARG3 (c4 / cautious-02
                              :ARG0 p)
                        :time (a / ahead
                              :op1 (d3 / data
                                    :ARG1-of (k / key-02)
                                    :mod c
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "U.S.")))))))
